WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.350 --> 02:49.910
[Episode 12]

02:50.530 --> 02:52.329
I hope you can tell me

02:52.350 --> 02:53.480
everything you know,

02:53.500 --> 02:54.820
including your past.

02:54.850 --> 02:56.230
Does my past

02:56.360 --> 02:58.320
have anything to do with what's happening now?

02:58.340 --> 02:59.290
You need to say it

02:59.320 --> 03:00.990
so we can know if it's relevant or not.

03:01.210 --> 03:02.400
Do it for Fan Yue.

03:02.430 --> 03:03.740
Don't use Master as an excuse.

03:04.040 --> 03:05.770
Even if he's lost his memory,

03:05.820 --> 03:07.700
he's not someone you can use.

03:08.210 --> 03:09.630
I have no intention of using him.

03:09.710 --> 03:11.380
I'm not an ungrateful person.

03:11.810 --> 03:13.260
Fan Yue saved me several times.

03:13.330 --> 03:14.520
I feel indebted to him

03:14.570 --> 03:15.810
and don't want him to die.

03:16.060 --> 03:17.980
But the one you should be worrying about is not me

03:18.010 --> 03:18.920
but him.

03:19.620 --> 03:21.200
Reopening the Wutong Contest

03:21.270 --> 03:23.390
was originally a deal between Fan Yue and the King of Outlanders.

03:23.410 --> 03:25.620
But now, the King has actually turned against him

03:25.650 --> 03:26.880
and sent people to kill him.

03:26.900 --> 03:28.550
Something must have changed.

03:29.260 --> 03:30.890
We don't know

03:30.910 --> 03:31.920
what's happening behind the scenes,

03:32.190 --> 03:33.570
and we don't know

03:33.600 --> 03:34.890
what will happen next.

03:34.920 --> 03:36.710
But all the clues point

03:36.730 --> 03:38.380
to one time:

03:39.130 --> 03:40.270
seven years ago.

03:43.079 --> 03:44.000
Seven years ago,

03:44.030 --> 03:45.140
you left the Outlanders' City.

03:45.730 --> 03:46.600
Seven years ago,

03:46.620 --> 03:47.780
the King sealed the City

03:47.800 --> 03:49.079
and canceled the Wutong Contest.

03:49.110 --> 03:50.270
And seven years ago,

03:50.290 --> 03:51.920
a monster appeared in the City.

03:52.210 --> 03:54.370
These things must be connected.

03:54.390 --> 03:55.550
If you don't know the answer,

03:55.579 --> 03:57.310
we can search for it together.

04:00.770 --> 04:01.680
Tian Huo,

04:02.680 --> 04:04.100
you don't have to like me,

04:04.770 --> 04:06.530
but can you trust me just this once?

04:18.480 --> 04:20.070
Have you heard of the Outlander King's Sword?

04:22.300 --> 04:23.430
Seven years ago,

04:24.340 --> 04:25.970
I wanted to use the Outlander King's Sword

04:26.480 --> 04:27.740
to destroy the City.

04:28.250 --> 04:29.200
What?

04:29.350 --> 04:30.580
The King of Outlanders

04:30.720 --> 04:32.780
is not a simple hereditary title.

04:32.810 --> 04:34.730
It's passed down with the Outlander King's Sword.

04:34.930 --> 04:36.510
Legend has it that the first King of Outlanders

04:36.600 --> 04:37.960
found pieces of divine meteorite

04:37.990 --> 04:39.450
in the Eastern Sea

04:39.659 --> 04:41.680
and forged them into the Outlander King's Sword.

04:41.700 --> 04:43.140
With the power of the Sword,

04:43.180 --> 04:44.710
he built the Outlanders' City

04:44.920 --> 04:47.120
and gave the Outlanders a home.

04:47.930 --> 04:50.730
The Sword gives the Outlanders' City vitality.

04:51.010 --> 04:52.070
But the Sword's power

04:52.250 --> 04:53.760
is not infinite.

04:54.540 --> 04:55.980
Every ten years,

04:56.010 --> 04:57.830
the King of Outlanders must pull the Sword out

04:57.850 --> 04:59.790
and temper it with his own blood

04:59.810 --> 05:02.250
to restore its energy.

05:02.610 --> 05:04.410
When the throne was passed to Hua Lin,

05:04.440 --> 05:05.730
he couldn't hold onto it

05:05.910 --> 05:07.590
because he was born weak

05:07.610 --> 05:09.190
and couldn't pull the Sword out.

05:10.240 --> 05:12.610
Then how did Hua Lin become the King?

05:12.950 --> 05:15.120
In the City, besides the Hua family as the royal lineage,

05:16.200 --> 05:17.880
there is another big family, the Mei family.

05:18.920 --> 05:21.580
For generations, the Mei family has shouldered the duty

05:21.600 --> 05:23.130
of supporting the Hua family and defending the City.

05:23.450 --> 05:24.800
In that generation,

05:25.180 --> 05:27.090
General Mei had only one daughter

05:27.190 --> 05:28.120
named Han.

05:28.780 --> 05:31.670
The old King of Outlanders made a deal with General Mei

05:32.060 --> 05:34.300
to ensure the Hua family could stay on the throne.

05:34.780 --> 05:36.090
What kind of deal?

05:36.120 --> 05:38.280
Hua Lin would marry Mei Han as the crown princess,

05:38.980 --> 05:40.090
and the Mei family

05:40.750 --> 05:42.710
would offer General Mei's spiritual power

05:43.010 --> 05:44.340
to Hua Lin

05:44.510 --> 05:46.570
to rebuild his weak body.

05:47.250 --> 05:49.140
General Mei died because of this.

05:49.440 --> 05:51.430
Hua Lin's spiritual veins were reforged.

05:51.480 --> 05:52.840
He drew the Outlander King's Sword

05:52.950 --> 05:54.620
and became the new King of Outlanders.

05:54.880 --> 05:57.510
Not long after, he fulfilled his promise and married Mei Han.

05:58.250 --> 06:02.260
[After the queen falls, the famine will be gone.]

05:59.540 --> 06:02.090
Everything changed seven years ago.

06:02.670 --> 06:04.570
That year, a famine broke out in the Outlanders' City.

06:05.550 --> 06:06.920
In the dry riverbed,

06:07.210 --> 06:08.510
a boulder suddenly appeared,

06:08.530 --> 06:10.410
carved with a so-called divine prophecy.

06:12.080 --> 06:13.490
"After the queen falls,

06:13.740 --> 06:15.090
the famine will be gone."

06:16.060 --> 06:17.910
Those nine words

06:17.940 --> 06:19.970
sentenced my mother to death.

06:20.830 --> 06:21.890
Burn her, burn her!

06:21.920 --> 06:24.020
Everyone went mad,

06:23.200 --> 06:25.410
[Mei Han, Outlander Race, Queen of Outlanders]

06:24.360 --> 06:26.300
demanding my mother be sacrificed

06:26.320 --> 06:27.590
to end the disaster.

06:28.860 --> 06:30.520
Even though this queen

06:31.620 --> 06:33.780
was once loved by all of them.

06:35.950 --> 06:38.870
♫I remember that moonlit night♫

06:36.260 --> 06:37.870
At first, Hua Lin hesitated

06:38.820 --> 06:40.770
and hid my mother in a secret place.

06:39.650 --> 06:42.190
♫The flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime♫

06:40.790 --> 06:41.760
Mother!

06:41.790 --> 06:44.300
But Hua Yong exposed her whereabouts.

06:42.860 --> 06:46.770
♫I remember that word of concern♫

06:44.320 --> 06:45.080
Let go of me!

06:45.110 --> 06:46.159
Let go!

06:46.580 --> 06:48.310
The people threatened

06:47.400 --> 06:50.640
♫But unfortunately, I didn't get to answer♫

06:48.340 --> 06:49.980
to overthrow Hua Lin

06:50.290 --> 06:51.659
if he didn't sacrifice the queen.

06:51.140 --> 06:53.950
♫I remember that drop of tear♫

06:51.690 --> 06:53.250
No!

06:54.350 --> 06:55.830
Hua Lin got the throne

06:54.710 --> 06:58.100
♫It dried in the wind♫

06:55.970 --> 06:58.770
at the cost of my grandfather's life.

06:58.780 --> 07:00.430
♫The one in the autumn wind♫

06:59.960 --> 07:01.520
To him,

07:00.960 --> 07:04.550
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

07:01.650 --> 07:03.530
power was the most important.

07:05.460 --> 07:08.850
♫That year, that year♫

07:06.210 --> 07:08.280
To avoid being overthrown by his people,

07:08.490 --> 07:10.450
he allowed it all to happen.

07:09.390 --> 07:12.600
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

07:11.010 --> 07:11.850
Hua Lin,

07:11.880 --> 07:12.940
I hate you!

07:13.010 --> 07:15.080
Give me my mother back!

07:13.220 --> 07:16.730
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

07:17.010 --> 07:18.590
Hua Lin lied to me.

07:17.370 --> 07:20.070
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

07:20.230 --> 07:21.940
He didn't step forward to protect her.

07:20.810 --> 07:24.130
♫That year, that year♫

07:21.960 --> 07:23.920
To preserve his throne,

07:24.050 --> 07:26.400
he watched his own queen

07:24.570 --> 07:27.910
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

07:26.430 --> 07:27.720
walk to her death.

07:28.370 --> 07:29.590
After my mother died,

07:28.460 --> 07:31.690
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

07:29.850 --> 07:31.230
I was utterly broken.

07:31.820 --> 07:33.340
The Outlanders demanded her death.

07:32.840 --> 07:35.570
♫Layer after layer♫

07:34.000 --> 07:35.530
Hua Yong caused her death.

07:35.850 --> 07:37.409
Hua Lin abandoned her.

07:36.070 --> 07:39.130
♫Another year passed♫

07:38.460 --> 07:39.659
At that time, I thought

07:40.720 --> 07:43.159
they all deserved to be buried with her!

07:44.640 --> 07:46.570
So I stormed into the sword vault.

07:47.380 --> 07:49.580
I wanted to destroy the Outlander King's Sword

07:50.090 --> 07:51.240
and the Outlanders' City.

07:51.240 --> 07:52.480
Sister, stop!

07:54.680 --> 07:56.210
The Sword is the foundation of the City.

07:56.240 --> 07:58.110
If you destroy it, the City will fall.

07:58.930 --> 07:59.870
Get lost!

08:00.560 --> 08:03.130
If you hadn't revealed Mother's whereabouts,

08:03.170 --> 08:04.590
she wouldn't have died!

08:05.840 --> 08:06.370
I...

08:06.390 --> 08:07.640
I didn't mean to.

08:07.670 --> 08:08.820
Shut up!

08:09.300 --> 08:10.770
Don't think I don't know.

08:11.710 --> 08:14.110
If Hua Lin was overthrown,

08:14.130 --> 08:16.290
you, as the crown prince, would lose everything too.

08:16.320 --> 08:17.250
You couldn't bear that!

08:17.270 --> 08:17.910
It's not true.

08:20.250 --> 08:22.590
I want everyone to be buried with her!

08:45.310 --> 08:46.830
In the end, I failed.

08:47.820 --> 08:49.400
I couldn't destroy the Outlanders' City.

08:50.040 --> 08:51.090
So,

08:51.750 --> 08:53.120
you left the Outlanders' City

08:53.510 --> 08:54.790
and never wanted to return.

08:55.240 --> 08:56.740
When I woke up,

08:57.320 --> 08:59.030
I was already outside the City.

08:59.910 --> 09:01.670
They threw me out

09:01.690 --> 09:02.930
and completely abandoned me.

09:04.040 --> 09:05.790
The solution you're looking for

09:05.990 --> 09:07.270
is not in my past.

09:09.310 --> 09:10.030
Not necessarily.

09:14.510 --> 09:15.030
Who's there?

09:20.440 --> 09:21.420
It's you.

09:22.350 --> 09:23.590
How much did you hear?

09:25.000 --> 09:26.210
I was just passing by.

09:26.240 --> 09:27.410
I didn't hear anything.

09:28.890 --> 09:29.890
Fine. I'll tell you.

09:29.910 --> 09:31.390
I saw your impressive spiritual power

09:31.420 --> 09:32.940
and came to ask for guidance.

09:32.960 --> 09:34.210
I really didn't hear much.

09:34.240 --> 09:35.520
How much is "not much?"

09:37.240 --> 09:38.440
Probably from the part

09:38.830 --> 09:40.530
where you mentioned the Outlander King's Sword.

09:40.710 --> 09:41.950
So that's everything.

09:42.470 --> 09:43.100
Ms. Bai.

09:43.130 --> 09:44.090
Help me!

09:44.200 --> 09:45.180
He's the Young Master of the Fox Clan.

09:45.200 --> 09:46.510
You can't kill him.

09:46.530 --> 09:47.370
I won't kill him.

09:47.400 --> 09:48.650
I'll just cripple him.

09:49.220 --> 09:49.730
Bai Shuo!

09:49.760 --> 09:50.330
Bai Shuo!

09:50.350 --> 09:51.030
What's wrong?

09:51.060 --> 09:51.940
Master is not doing well.

10:00.330 --> 10:01.230
Yue.

10:01.250 --> 10:02.800
I'm Grandfather.

10:02.820 --> 10:04.720
I'm Qi Feng.

10:05.620 --> 10:06.740
From now on,

10:06.770 --> 10:07.900
Yue

10:07.920 --> 10:10.330
must stay safe and sound,

10:10.350 --> 10:12.290
free from illness and misfortune.

10:16.410 --> 10:17.060
No.

10:17.170 --> 10:18.300
Grandfather!

10:18.320 --> 10:19.530
Grandfather!

10:19.960 --> 10:20.890
No!

10:22.530 --> 10:23.260
No.

10:24.960 --> 10:25.680
Master.

10:28.250 --> 10:28.940
Shuo.

10:38.480 --> 10:39.630
Mu Jiu

10:39.660 --> 10:40.920
left so quickly.

10:41.780 --> 10:42.550
Tian Huo.

10:46.280 --> 10:47.060
They...

10:47.370 --> 10:48.490
Why did you push me out?

10:48.510 --> 10:50.840
Master trusts Bai Shuo the most now.

10:50.870 --> 10:51.990
Leave her to it.

10:53.170 --> 10:54.610
What's wrong with you?

10:54.650 --> 10:55.730
Did you have a nightmare?

10:56.930 --> 10:58.120
I saw blood.

10:58.890 --> 11:00.260
Blood everywhere.

11:00.820 --> 11:02.060
They were all dead.

11:02.700 --> 11:03.630
Who was dead?

11:04.620 --> 11:05.190
Grandfather.

11:06.960 --> 11:07.850
Qi Feng.

11:08.340 --> 11:09.370
Grandfather,

11:09.600 --> 11:10.730
Qi Feng?

11:11.170 --> 11:12.770
And many others—people I don't even know.

11:12.800 --> 11:14.160
But they were all dead.

11:16.830 --> 11:19.040
[Qi Feng]

11:20.810 --> 11:23.050
So those nameplates in the secret chamber

11:23.080 --> 11:24.960
are for his departed loved ones.

11:25.440 --> 11:27.730
How much pain must he have endured back then

11:28.000 --> 11:29.520
to make it this far?

11:31.330 --> 11:32.160
Shuo.

11:32.190 --> 11:33.330
When I saw them die

11:33.370 --> 11:34.630
in front of me one by one,

11:35.510 --> 11:36.680
it hurt…

11:36.700 --> 11:37.700
so much here.

11:38.380 --> 11:39.740
Why did they have to kill them?

11:41.020 --> 11:42.800
Why am I the only one left?

11:46.720 --> 11:48.520
They're just people in your dream.

11:49.340 --> 11:50.550
It's over now,

11:50.960 --> 11:52.200
so don't dwell on it.

11:53.530 --> 11:54.570
People in my dream?

11:56.240 --> 11:57.340
People in your dream.

11:57.620 --> 11:59.420
Although they won't appear again,

12:00.090 --> 12:01.760
somewhere you can't see,

12:02.520 --> 12:04.310
they'll be silently watching over you.

12:04.850 --> 12:06.730
Do you have someone in your dream too?

12:10.640 --> 12:11.470
Yes.

12:12.700 --> 12:14.160
He's always

12:14.800 --> 12:16.090
in my dream.

12:17.700 --> 12:19.300
Does it hurt you too?

12:20.270 --> 12:20.960
Yes.

12:22.610 --> 12:24.180
When I lost him,

12:25.550 --> 12:27.560
it was so painful that I thought I couldn't go on.

12:28.760 --> 12:30.790
But looking back,

12:31.780 --> 12:33.180
I've realized that

12:33.940 --> 12:35.960
since we're the ones still alive,

12:36.580 --> 12:38.800
we should live well

12:41.110 --> 12:42.260
for them

12:42.850 --> 12:44.090
and for ourselves.

12:47.970 --> 12:49.760
I'm glad I have you, Shuo.

12:55.210 --> 12:56.600
Does Bai Shuo truly care for Master,

12:56.600 --> 12:57.920
or is she pretending?

12:57.940 --> 12:59.110
Keep an eye on Master.

12:59.140 --> 13:00.040
I'm going out.

13:00.060 --> 13:00.730
Where to?

13:00.760 --> 13:01.650
The Outlander Palace.

13:02.040 --> 13:03.250
They've already sent assassins.

13:03.270 --> 13:04.520
They won't show you mercy.

13:04.550 --> 13:05.400
Perfect.

13:05.420 --> 13:07.290
I won't show them mercy either.

13:07.630 --> 13:09.320
How dare they harm Master?

13:09.340 --> 13:10.540
It's unforgivable.

13:11.370 --> 13:11.850
Tian Huo.

13:12.480 --> 13:13.200
Tian Huo!

13:13.220 --> 13:14.380
Keep an eye on Master.

13:53.730 --> 13:55.130
I've been looking for you everywhere.

13:55.210 --> 13:56.710
So you're hiding here.

13:59.800 --> 14:01.610
She's long dead because of you.

14:01.940 --> 14:03.730
Now you're pretending to mourn

14:03.750 --> 14:06.220
and acting all fake. Who are you trying to fool?

14:18.900 --> 14:20.520
This is my mother's courtyard.

14:20.750 --> 14:23.450
You don't deserve to touch the tree she planted!

14:23.470 --> 14:24.790
You're later

14:25.170 --> 14:26.670
than I expected.

14:27.340 --> 14:28.190
What?

14:28.220 --> 14:30.300
Were you too busy saving

14:30.360 --> 14:31.920
the Master of Bright Moon Palace?

14:32.180 --> 14:33.950
You've always tried to stay out of trouble,

14:34.360 --> 14:36.940
but now you openly go against Bright Moon Palace.

14:37.400 --> 14:39.100
Looks like you've got some backing.

14:39.310 --> 14:40.950
Ever since the Eternals and demons entered the City,

14:40.970 --> 14:42.330
everything that's happened

14:42.360 --> 14:43.840
is planned by you and the one behind you.

14:43.870 --> 14:44.750
Tell me.

14:45.170 --> 14:47.740
What's your scheme?

14:47.830 --> 14:49.220
Since it's a scheme,

14:49.440 --> 14:50.890
I'm not going to tell you.

14:51.260 --> 14:53.140
I warned you before—

14:53.170 --> 14:54.340
leave the Outlanders' City

14:54.510 --> 14:55.960
and never come back.

14:56.210 --> 14:57.950
For the sake of your mother,

14:58.270 --> 14:59.200
I'll spare your life

14:59.220 --> 15:01.130
one last time

15:01.160 --> 15:02.600
as long as you listen to me.

15:02.630 --> 15:03.750
Spare my life?

15:04.350 --> 15:05.920
You don't get to do that.

15:07.250 --> 15:09.660
I'll kill whoever wants to kill Master.

15:10.020 --> 15:11.980
Do you really think you can beat me?

15:12.180 --> 15:13.790
Have you forgotten how you got

15:13.790 --> 15:14.670
your spiritual power?

15:15.580 --> 15:16.630
If my grandfather hadn't

15:16.650 --> 15:18.130
passed on all his spiritual power to you,

15:18.160 --> 15:19.710
you'd have lost your throne long ago.

15:20.380 --> 15:21.240
Today,

15:21.760 --> 15:24.450
I'm taking back what belongs to the Mei family.

15:37.150 --> 15:38.390
Another one?

15:38.830 --> 15:39.620
Perfect.

15:40.110 --> 15:42.060
No one can leave tonight.

15:42.210 --> 15:43.200
Princess,

15:43.400 --> 15:44.350
His Majesty already held back

15:44.370 --> 15:45.770
in the strike just now.

15:45.800 --> 15:46.420
Don't trespass on

15:46.450 --> 15:48.260
the last bit of his affection for you.

15:48.300 --> 15:49.150
Please leave.

15:49.170 --> 15:50.210
Stop acting!

15:50.230 --> 15:51.280
The monster you raise

15:51.310 --> 15:52.620
secretly created evil cultivators,

15:52.640 --> 15:55.160
and yet you claim to care about your people.

15:55.190 --> 15:57.090
I don't care what your scheme is,

15:57.240 --> 15:58.540
but since you've hurt Master,

15:58.760 --> 16:00.500
no matter the cost,

16:00.690 --> 16:02.400
I'll kill you.

16:07.980 --> 16:08.880
You're wrong!

16:09.060 --> 16:10.580
I didn't create the monster.

16:10.910 --> 16:11.830
You did!

16:27.600 --> 16:30.420
You're actually using the sword vault to create evil cultivators?

16:32.670 --> 16:34.200
You said I made this monster.

16:35.410 --> 16:36.760
Why is that?

17:46.740 --> 17:48.220
Hua Yong?

17:48.860 --> 17:50.190
How did this happen?

17:50.220 --> 17:51.480
I saw him at the inn before.

17:51.480 --> 17:52.550
He was perfectly fine.

17:54.530 --> 17:55.640
What did you do to him?

17:55.750 --> 17:57.100
What did we do?

17:58.550 --> 18:00.630
Didn't you see it with your own eyes?

18:01.880 --> 18:03.520
His Majesty used his own blood

18:03.380 --> 18:08.520
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

18:03.650 --> 18:05.610
to make the crown prince normal again.

18:05.770 --> 18:06.610
Over the years,

18:06.640 --> 18:08.950
if not for His Majesty feeding the prince with his blood,

18:09.570 --> 18:11.180
he would've long lost his sanity

18:11.210 --> 18:12.850
and turned into a complete monster.

18:11.520 --> 18:17.290
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

18:13.840 --> 18:16.060
How else do you think he could hold back when facing you?

18:16.640 --> 18:18.050
During the day, Hua Yong

18:18.080 --> 18:19.470
is no different from a normal person.

18:19.750 --> 18:27.200
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

18:20.570 --> 18:22.060
But at night,

18:22.090 --> 18:23.490
after he falls asleep,

18:24.260 --> 18:25.910
he turns into a monster.

18:26.150 --> 18:27.720
What exactly happened?

18:28.070 --> 18:33.400
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

18:28.200 --> 18:29.840
What does it have to do with me?

18:30.880 --> 18:32.390
Have you forgotten

18:32.420 --> 18:33.630
what you did?

18:33.880 --> 18:35.010
Seven years ago,

18:35.030 --> 18:36.580
you stormed into the Underground Palace,

18:36.610 --> 18:38.200
trying to destroy the Outlander King's Sword.

18:44.530 --> 18:45.290
Sister.

18:55.330 --> 18:58.860
♫Across thousands of miles♫

19:00.230 --> 19:01.230
Sister.

19:03.770 --> 19:08.450
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

19:05.690 --> 19:07.180
You can't die.

19:10.670 --> 19:14.230
Hua Yong shielded you from the attack of the Sword

19:11.330 --> 19:18.510
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

19:14.980 --> 19:16.970
and pulled out his spiritual bone

19:17.540 --> 19:19.750
to save you.

19:19.370 --> 19:24.200
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

19:27.920 --> 19:29.880
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

19:30.080 --> 19:32.120
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

19:32.180 --> 19:33.970
♫My love brought tears♫

19:34.220 --> 19:35.940
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

19:36.370 --> 19:38.190
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

19:38.400 --> 19:39.820
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

19:40.030 --> 19:41.650
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

19:41.750 --> 19:44.190
With that extra spiritual bone in your body,

19:42.020 --> 19:44.000
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

19:44.350 --> 19:45.940
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

19:44.540 --> 19:47.380
you were able to break through the cultivation limits of Outlanders.

19:46.190 --> 19:47.840
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

19:47.990 --> 19:49.290
But Hua Yong,

19:48.110 --> 19:50.220
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

19:49.610 --> 19:51.540
without his spiritual bone,

19:50.530 --> 19:52.110
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

19:51.570 --> 19:54.050
couldn't resist the sword energy's devoration

19:52.430 --> 19:54.220
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

19:54.070 --> 19:55.680
and turned into a monster.

19:54.490 --> 19:56.500
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

19:56.390 --> 19:58.500
Everything you have today

19:56.790 --> 19:58.290
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

19:58.490 --> 20:00.950
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

19:58.720 --> 20:01.310
was bought with Hua Yong's life.

20:04.680 --> 20:07.030
There's only one way to save him.

20:07.720 --> 20:08.550
What is it?

20:08.970 --> 20:10.230
The Contemplation Stone.

20:11.360 --> 20:12.730
What do you want?

20:14.350 --> 20:15.670
I want Bai Shuo.

20:16.080 --> 20:18.520
Master would never let you take Bai Shuo.

20:19.130 --> 20:19.920
And I'll never disobey

20:20.510 --> 20:22.060
his orders.

20:22.380 --> 20:24.200
The Outlanders' City forbids all magic,

20:25.570 --> 20:27.360
and Fan Yue is already gravely injured.

20:27.380 --> 20:28.700
He has no strength left to fight.

20:28.840 --> 20:30.150
If you hand over Bai Shuo to me,

20:30.600 --> 20:32.150
I'll spare Fan Yue's life.

20:32.590 --> 20:33.200
Otherwise,

20:34.060 --> 20:36.950
none of you can leave the City alive.

20:38.740 --> 20:40.580
One is your master who saved your life,

20:40.610 --> 20:42.590
and the other is your brother who gave you his spiritual bone.

20:43.030 --> 20:44.790
Do they both

20:44.820 --> 20:45.680
mean less to you

20:45.680 --> 20:47.830
than Bai Shuo, who has no blood ties to you?

20:47.860 --> 20:49.180
Weigh the stakes,

20:49.480 --> 20:50.950
Lady Tian Huo,

20:50.970 --> 20:52.170
and make your choice.

21:35.110 --> 21:35.680
Mas…

21:40.380 --> 21:41.250
Master is asleep?

21:44.870 --> 21:46.390
Did your master used to

21:46.410 --> 21:47.680
have nightmares too?

21:47.700 --> 21:49.460
In the past, Master never slept deeply,

21:49.490 --> 21:50.960
so he never had dreams.

21:50.980 --> 21:52.170
Never slept deeply?

21:52.390 --> 21:53.720
Being the Demon King of the Polar Region

21:53.740 --> 21:55.250
means he could never let his guard down.

21:55.780 --> 21:56.830
As demons,

21:56.950 --> 21:58.820
we've fought through countless battles.

21:59.080 --> 22:00.750
You'll never understand

22:01.000 --> 22:02.440
what Master has gone through.

22:09.390 --> 22:10.320
Where have you been?

22:16.440 --> 22:18.290
Why are you staring at me like that?

22:18.970 --> 22:21.130
If I say I want your life,

22:21.570 --> 22:22.690
will you give it to me?

22:35.400 --> 22:37.260
I told you to keep an eye on Yong.

22:37.280 --> 22:38.730
How did he suddenly appear?

22:39.060 --> 22:40.220
I don't know.

22:40.990 --> 22:42.340
Perhaps it's the bond of blood.

22:42.360 --> 22:44.160
The crown prince sensed his sister,

22:44.290 --> 22:46.660
or maybe he sensed that you were in danger.

22:50.530 --> 22:51.640
I didn't plan

22:51.640 --> 22:53.350
to let her know about Yong.

22:54.060 --> 22:54.960
Your Majesty,

22:54.980 --> 22:55.850
what she's meant to know,

22:55.970 --> 22:56.820
she'll find out sooner or later.

22:57.380 --> 22:58.350
What do you think

22:59.090 --> 23:00.250
she'll choose?

23:00.280 --> 23:01.350
Whatever her choice,

23:01.450 --> 23:02.970
as long as they want the Heart Flame,

23:03.170 --> 23:04.800
they'll definitely come to the Fenlan Banquet.

23:06.040 --> 23:07.750
Send word to Zhen Yu.

23:07.910 --> 23:09.390
Tell him to come

23:09.410 --> 23:10.410
after the Fenlan Banquet

23:10.440 --> 23:11.750
to get what he wants.

23:11.870 --> 23:12.460
Yes.

23:13.050 --> 23:14.050
You just lost blood.

23:14.070 --> 23:15.450
Your spiritual power has been weakened.

23:16.070 --> 23:17.310
Please take a good rest.

23:23.790 --> 23:24.800
So,

23:24.970 --> 23:26.820
you misunderstood Hua Yong back then.

23:27.660 --> 23:29.970
Someone who risked his life to protect his sister

23:30.000 --> 23:32.160
would never betray his own mother

23:32.180 --> 23:33.630
for wealth and power.

23:37.180 --> 23:38.860
Since you're loyal to Fan Yue

23:38.890 --> 23:40.010
and feel guilty toward Hua Yong,

23:40.120 --> 23:41.490
why don't you just agree

23:41.520 --> 23:42.470
to the King's terms

23:42.490 --> 23:43.490
and hand me over?

23:43.760 --> 23:44.920
I don't want to do that.

23:45.110 --> 23:46.070
You don't want to?

23:47.650 --> 23:49.330
Lady Tian Huo, I doubt your feelings

23:49.360 --> 23:51.100
for me run that deep.

23:51.380 --> 23:52.620
Bright Moon Palace

23:52.650 --> 23:54.090
will never bow to Hua Lin.

23:55.140 --> 23:56.500
As for our predicament,

23:56.820 --> 23:58.560
I don't believe there is only one solution.

23:58.630 --> 23:59.910
You don't believe that either,

23:59.930 --> 24:00.600
do you?

24:02.370 --> 24:04.070
I never thought

24:04.160 --> 24:05.510
it would take something like this

24:05.510 --> 24:07.200
to get a bit of acknowledgment from you.

24:08.290 --> 24:09.960
But there's one thing I don't understand.

24:10.830 --> 24:12.480
If, as Hua Lin said,

24:12.480 --> 24:13.910
he's trying to save Hua Yong,

24:14.000 --> 24:15.610
the first thing he should have done

24:15.640 --> 24:18.300
is take back the spiritual bone from you.

24:18.320 --> 24:19.710
But he hasn't.

24:19.740 --> 24:20.810
Isn't that strange?

24:20.830 --> 24:22.560
He didn't tell me much.

24:22.980 --> 24:24.510
The Outlanders' City

24:24.820 --> 24:26.410
is no longer the same as it once was.

24:26.870 --> 24:28.670
Too many secrets are hidden in the dark.

24:29.580 --> 24:30.790
There's another question.

24:31.710 --> 24:33.910
If Hua Lin only wanted the Contemplation Stone,

24:33.930 --> 24:35.540
he could have captured me directly.

24:35.900 --> 24:37.510
Why go through such a convoluted plan?

24:37.940 --> 24:39.610
When we got the second Heart Flame,

24:39.640 --> 24:41.560
if not for Fan Yue sacrificing his own spiritual power

24:41.580 --> 24:42.900
to break Rong Xian's realm of resentment,

24:42.930 --> 24:44.450
I might be trapped there forever,

24:44.470 --> 24:46.100
and he'd never get the Contemplation Stone.

24:46.570 --> 24:47.750
Unless...

24:47.780 --> 24:48.850
Unless

24:48.870 --> 24:50.210
part of his plan

24:50.550 --> 24:51.200
requires us

24:51.200 --> 24:53.440
to dispel Rong Xian's resentment.

24:53.860 --> 24:54.640
Exactly.

24:56.670 --> 24:57.880
Hua Lin must be

24:57.930 --> 24:59.710
hiding more secrets.

25:06.570 --> 25:07.760
Blood formation…

25:09.090 --> 25:10.160
Altar?

25:12.430 --> 25:13.510
What are you doing?

25:13.840 --> 25:14.520
Yong.

25:15.240 --> 25:16.350
You heard everything?

25:16.930 --> 25:17.740
Don't be afraid.

25:18.190 --> 25:19.350
I'm saving you.

25:19.370 --> 25:20.270
Saving me?

25:21.660 --> 25:23.480
Using blood for formations is forbidden magic.

25:23.870 --> 25:24.800
What's wrong with me

25:25.590 --> 25:26.940
that you need to save me like this?

25:27.330 --> 25:28.670
Wait until tomorrow night.

25:29.020 --> 25:30.710
When everything is over,

25:31.060 --> 25:32.410
I'll tell you everything.

25:36.000 --> 25:37.920
Since several years ago,

25:38.080 --> 25:39.400
I've been having strange

25:39.430 --> 25:41.780
nighttime visions from time to time.

25:42.460 --> 25:43.820
You said they were just dreams,

25:44.350 --> 25:45.720
but they were not,

25:46.240 --> 25:47.110
were they?

25:48.280 --> 25:50.850
Seven years ago, I shielded my sister from the Sword's attack,

25:50.880 --> 25:52.600
but I showed no symptoms of devoration.

25:52.990 --> 25:54.880
You said it was because you made me take some pill,

25:54.880 --> 25:55.720
but that wasn't true either,

25:55.720 --> 25:56.510
was it?

25:58.850 --> 26:01.120
A monster has been lurking in the City for seven years,

26:01.150 --> 26:02.650
and it's still not been caught.

26:03.270 --> 26:04.530
And for these seven years,

26:05.100 --> 26:07.700
I can't remember what happened at night.

26:07.970 --> 26:10.050
It's because I am the monster,

26:10.320 --> 26:11.390
right?

26:13.720 --> 26:15.490
What's the point of knowing all this?

26:15.850 --> 26:17.050
All you need to know is that

26:17.700 --> 26:19.370
I will save you.

26:19.400 --> 26:21.030
But sustaining life with blood is forbidden.

26:21.390 --> 26:22.670
If the Eternals and demons find out,

26:22.690 --> 26:23.930
the Outlanders' City will fall!

26:23.960 --> 26:25.530
Then let them disappear first.

26:25.550 --> 26:27.140
If they disappear,

26:27.170 --> 26:28.660
who can destroy the Outlanders' City?

26:29.410 --> 26:30.540
What are you planning?

26:31.220 --> 26:32.690
There is an ancient formation

26:32.780 --> 26:34.170
that uses Eternals and demons as sacrifices

26:34.200 --> 26:35.460
to create a deity.

26:35.700 --> 26:36.780
Create a deity?

26:50.750 --> 26:52.400
Those Eternals and demons think

26:52.510 --> 26:54.310
that by dispelling Rong Xian's resentment,

26:54.340 --> 26:55.580
they can rest easy.

26:55.600 --> 26:57.080
What a bunch of ignorant fools.

26:57.110 --> 26:57.940
This time,

26:57.960 --> 26:59.990
I truly have to thank Fan Yue and Bai Shuo.

27:00.010 --> 27:01.730
If they hadn't dispelled Rong Xian's resentment,

27:01.760 --> 27:03.930
I wouldn't be able to open the ancient barrier here.

27:04.630 --> 27:05.880
Where is the barrier?

27:05.900 --> 27:07.210
I don't see it.

27:07.240 --> 27:08.370
The core of the barrier

27:08.390 --> 27:10.060
is sealed beneath Rong Xian's tomb.

27:10.080 --> 27:11.640
The Formation Key from Grand Master

27:11.670 --> 27:13.680
can help me open the core.

27:13.710 --> 27:14.950
Once the barrier is opened,

27:14.970 --> 27:16.690
the entire Outlanders' City will be covered.

27:16.720 --> 27:18.130
No one can get in,

27:18.160 --> 27:20.290
and no one can get out.

27:20.320 --> 27:22.110
Then those Eternals and demons in the City

27:22.140 --> 27:23.140
will be

27:23.160 --> 27:24.190
completely

27:24.220 --> 27:25.560
helpless.

27:25.580 --> 27:26.790
What about Chong Zhao?

27:26.820 --> 27:28.430
Are you abandoning him?

27:28.810 --> 27:30.770
I've given him a way out.

27:30.790 --> 27:32.380
But since he wants to die,

27:32.410 --> 27:33.970
it's not my fault.

28:08.610 --> 28:09.630
Chong Zhao.

28:09.700 --> 28:10.840
What's wrong?

28:11.820 --> 28:12.650
Nothing.

28:12.990 --> 28:14.120
I just feel uneasy.

28:14.240 --> 28:16.240
I saw your lights still on

28:16.260 --> 28:17.740
and made you some calming tea.

28:18.370 --> 28:19.500
Thank you.

28:21.260 --> 28:22.020
Still no response

28:22.050 --> 28:23.200
from Sect Leader?

28:24.330 --> 28:26.650
Is it because he's been too busy with official matters?

28:26.670 --> 28:27.560
No matter how busy,

28:27.590 --> 28:29.340
with evil cultivators in the Outlanders' City,

28:29.370 --> 28:31.400
Master would never stand by and do nothing.

28:31.600 --> 28:32.320
I'll write another letter

28:32.350 --> 28:33.350
and personally send it to him.

28:37.780 --> 28:39.160
For a thousand years,

28:39.750 --> 28:41.630
the Outlanders have been trapped in an isolated city,

28:41.820 --> 28:43.200
struggling to survive.

28:43.670 --> 28:45.470
You're my heir.

28:46.030 --> 28:47.260
Only by becoming a deity

28:47.630 --> 28:49.470
can you have the power to defeat Eternals and demons

28:49.970 --> 28:51.560
and lead our people to rise

28:51.680 --> 28:53.510
and walk out with dignity.

28:53.560 --> 28:55.050
Sacrificing others

28:55.080 --> 28:56.520
to make me a deity?

28:56.680 --> 28:58.400
That's the way you've chosen?

29:00.700 --> 29:02.210
The existence of the City

29:02.940 --> 29:04.510
depends on the Outlander King's Sword.

29:05.290 --> 29:06.920
But I'm old now

29:06.940 --> 29:08.940
and can no longer pull the Sword out.

29:08.960 --> 29:11.280
Nor can I inject life into it again.

29:11.310 --> 29:12.660
If the Outlanders' City falls,

29:13.320 --> 29:14.970
where can our people go?

29:15.640 --> 29:16.880
But this time,

29:16.910 --> 29:18.720
with the help of the Master of Cold Spring Palace,

29:18.850 --> 29:20.700
who told me how to create a deity,

29:21.630 --> 29:23.320
I have to risk it all.

29:23.350 --> 29:24.680
The Master of Cold Spring Palace?

29:25.430 --> 29:26.640
He's the Demon King.

29:26.930 --> 29:28.210
If he could create a deity,

29:28.380 --> 29:29.390
why would he tell you

29:29.410 --> 29:30.620
instead of becoming a deity himself?

29:30.640 --> 29:32.320
I know he's up to something,

29:33.120 --> 29:34.810
but I have no other choice.

29:35.390 --> 29:37.190
Neither you nor the City has any time left.

29:37.700 --> 29:39.050
The Eternals and demons

29:39.120 --> 29:40.680
don't allow evil beings to exist.

29:41.330 --> 29:42.370
Seven years ago,

29:42.450 --> 29:43.840
when you began to change,

29:43.860 --> 29:45.070
I canceled the Wutong Contest

29:45.160 --> 29:46.540
and hid the Outlanders' City

29:46.920 --> 29:48.240
in order to protect you.

29:48.290 --> 29:49.590
Seven years have passed,

29:49.700 --> 29:51.620
and your condition has worsened,

29:51.730 --> 29:53.250
now endangering your life.

29:53.270 --> 29:54.750
I'm holding the Contest again

29:54.950 --> 29:56.250
to make you a deity.

29:56.310 --> 29:58.460
It's only for the Outlanders

29:58.610 --> 29:59.790
but also to save you.

30:00.050 --> 30:01.570
This is the only chance for survival.

30:01.590 --> 30:02.910
But this is evil!

30:03.210 --> 30:05.120
Nature has its own laws.

30:05.160 --> 30:07.560
Defying fate will only bring greater disasters.

30:07.580 --> 30:08.760
But if we don't do this,

30:08.940 --> 30:10.440
the only road ahead leads to death.

30:10.530 --> 30:11.640
Your death

30:11.940 --> 30:13.070
and the deaths of the Outlanders.

30:13.740 --> 30:15.460
Not all Eternals and demons are evil.

30:15.920 --> 30:17.360
Just because they're Eternals and demons,

30:17.380 --> 30:18.350
they deserve to die!

30:19.320 --> 30:20.270
What about my sister?

30:20.290 --> 30:21.830
She's sworn loyalty to the Master of Bright Moon Palace.

30:21.850 --> 30:23.090
Do you want to harm her?

30:30.980 --> 30:31.860
Yong.

30:33.120 --> 30:34.160
Wait one more day.

30:35.530 --> 30:36.770
One day later,

30:37.750 --> 30:39.340
with the Eternals and demons in the City as offerings,

30:40.830 --> 30:42.520
you can fully recover,

30:44.280 --> 30:45.160
and the Outlanders

30:46.440 --> 30:48.370
can be liberated once and for all.

30:54.060 --> 30:55.840
Divinity, you're in a hurry.

30:55.950 --> 30:57.410
Where are you going?

30:57.740 --> 30:58.450
Demon,

30:58.480 --> 30:59.280
it's you again.

30:59.360 --> 31:00.640
I've warned you—

31:00.670 --> 31:01.760
the Outlanders' City is dangerous,

31:01.780 --> 31:03.010
but you wouldn't listen.

31:03.030 --> 31:04.790
Now, even if you want to leave,

31:04.820 --> 31:06.120
you won't be able to.

31:06.820 --> 31:07.900
What do you mean?

31:07.930 --> 31:09.170
Nothing much.

31:09.190 --> 31:10.590
I just want to tell you

31:10.920 --> 31:12.350
the Outlanders' City

31:12.610 --> 31:14.090
is bound to meet its doom.

31:15.760 --> 31:16.670
But

31:17.170 --> 31:19.410
I do feel a bit reluctant to see you die.

31:20.220 --> 31:21.450
Still, the offer stands:

31:21.630 --> 31:23.310
If you're willing to leave your sect

31:23.340 --> 31:24.380
and join Cold Spring Palace,

31:24.570 --> 31:26.050
I might just

31:26.150 --> 31:28.000
spare your life.

31:28.020 --> 31:29.120
Dream on!

31:35.880 --> 31:36.590
You followed me?

31:36.620 --> 31:38.970
Bai Shuo told me you left the inn late at night

31:38.990 --> 31:39.950
and asked me to protect you,

31:40.210 --> 31:41.780
or I wouldn't have bothered.

31:42.870 --> 31:44.270
You really do keep being fooled

31:44.270 --> 31:45.500
by this demon woman.

31:45.520 --> 31:47.630
You've teamed up with Bright Moon Palace?

31:48.540 --> 31:49.680
You said you refuse to be a demon,

31:49.680 --> 31:51.110
but it turns out you just refuse

31:51.110 --> 31:52.350
to work with me.

31:53.090 --> 31:55.160
Is it because Bai Shuo is in Bright Moon Palace

31:55.190 --> 31:56.750
that you're willing to work with them?

31:56.770 --> 31:57.970
I was born an Eternal

31:58.000 --> 31:58.970
and will remain one for life.

31:59.080 --> 32:00.900
I'd never ally with the Demon Race.

32:01.220 --> 32:02.580
The Fenlan Banquet is tomorrow night.

32:02.600 --> 32:04.310
Cold Spring Palace is definitely scheming something.

32:04.340 --> 32:05.950
We must find it out tonight.

32:06.520 --> 32:07.720
Of course.

32:07.740 --> 32:08.890
She'll be interrogated.

32:09.550 --> 32:11.440
But since I captured her,

32:11.890 --> 32:13.290
we demons

32:13.320 --> 32:14.810
will handle the interrogation.

32:20.790 --> 32:22.510
Are you going to tell me,

32:22.590 --> 32:24.110
or should I make you?

32:24.630 --> 32:26.870
Should I call you Lady Tian Huo

32:26.890 --> 32:27.900
or...

32:28.760 --> 32:29.550
the Princess of Outlanders?

32:29.550 --> 32:30.670
Cut the crap!

32:30.700 --> 32:33.120
What's Cold Spring Palace plotting in the Outlanders' City?

32:33.260 --> 32:35.480
Are you working with the King of Outlanders?

32:36.850 --> 32:38.340
Go ask your father.

32:38.720 --> 32:39.570
By the way,

32:39.780 --> 32:41.070
don't think I don't know

32:41.240 --> 32:42.610
Fan Yue is no longer

32:42.640 --> 32:44.800
the same Master of Bright Moon Palace.

32:44.820 --> 32:46.820
Why do you have to die here with him?

32:47.700 --> 32:48.950
Speaking of which,

32:48.980 --> 32:50.230
Lady Tian Huo,

32:50.260 --> 32:51.690
you're very powerful.

32:51.710 --> 32:53.340
Why don't you consider joining Cold Spring Palace?

32:53.460 --> 32:54.960
Joining Cold Spring Palace?

32:55.810 --> 32:58.210
Those in Cold Spring Palace are all cold-blooded.

32:58.230 --> 33:00.280
You'll never understand the bonds we share in Bright Moon Palace.

33:03.160 --> 33:04.240
I told you,

33:04.270 --> 33:05.080
if I see you again,

33:05.100 --> 33:05.860
I'll kill you!

33:05.920 --> 33:06.640
Not yet.

33:06.670 --> 33:08.000
She hasn't told us about their scheme.

33:08.000 --> 33:09.000
No matter what their scheme is,

33:09.000 --> 33:10.420
I'll figure it out myself!

33:10.450 --> 33:12.260
You're still so full of yourself.

33:12.280 --> 33:13.990
Back in Ning'an City,

33:14.090 --> 33:16.010
you acted recklessly like this,

33:16.040 --> 33:17.880
thinking you could save your father.

33:18.080 --> 33:19.050
And what happened?

33:19.070 --> 33:20.470
You could only watch him die

33:20.490 --> 33:22.210
right in front of you.

33:23.220 --> 33:24.320
Shut up.

33:24.540 --> 33:25.800
When your father died,

33:25.830 --> 33:27.580
you couldn't do anything.

33:27.600 --> 33:29.530
Seeing you in great pain

33:29.590 --> 33:31.460
made me so happy.

33:37.790 --> 33:39.420
I said, shut up.

33:41.440 --> 33:42.520
Honestly,

33:43.300 --> 33:45.740
you should thank me for showing mercy

33:46.410 --> 33:48.180
and letting you meet your dad

33:48.340 --> 33:49.900
for the last time.

33:50.740 --> 33:52.930
He could rest in peace.

34:17.060 --> 34:18.790
I wonder if Lady Tian Huo is asleep yet.

34:19.040 --> 34:20.310
If I give her this gift,

34:20.389 --> 34:22.400
hopefully, she'll be willing to teach me some techniques.

34:30.139 --> 34:31.040
Who are you?

34:31.130 --> 34:32.210
How dare you kidnap the Young Master of the Fox Clan?

34:32.230 --> 34:32.870
Shut up!

34:33.050 --> 34:34.750
I'll turn you into a dead fox if you keep talking.

34:35.340 --> 34:36.900
You think you can escape?

34:36.920 --> 34:38.889
It's not bad to take someone with me before I die.

34:38.920 --> 34:40.920
He's the nephew of the Master of Jingyou Mountain.

34:40.940 --> 34:42.530
Aren't you afraid of Chang Mei leading the Fox Clan

34:42.560 --> 34:43.719
to destroy Cold Spring Palace?

34:43.739 --> 34:44.500
Exactly.

34:44.520 --> 34:45.120
My aunt will…

34:45.150 --> 34:46.989
If I were afraid of trouble, I would've long died.

34:47.040 --> 34:48.370
You guys should be worrying about

34:48.400 --> 34:50.070
whether you can make it out of this city alive.

34:59.060 --> 35:00.030
Ms. Bai,

35:00.380 --> 35:01.120
save me.

35:08.370 --> 35:09.300
See you again.

35:20.980 --> 35:22.220
That crazy woman…

35:25.070 --> 35:26.880
-It hurts so much!
-Why did you suddenly come?

35:27.140 --> 35:27.710
Do you know

35:27.710 --> 35:29.840
what kind of chance I've missed because of you?

35:35.560 --> 35:36.330
Ms. Bai.

35:37.500 --> 35:38.300
Tian Huo.

35:38.330 --> 35:39.370
What happened?

35:39.390 --> 35:40.550
Who were those two people?

35:40.580 --> 35:42.140
Why is Ms. Bai so angry?

35:43.440 --> 35:44.210
Tian Huo.

35:56.740 --> 35:58.000
I already know

35:58.100 --> 35:59.170
what happened just now.

36:00.340 --> 36:02.590
I should've killed her just now.

36:03.260 --> 36:05.500
That way, she wouldn't have had the chance to escape!

36:06.200 --> 36:06.950
Shuo.

36:07.920 --> 36:08.860
Have you ever killed anyone?

36:10.650 --> 36:11.670
Saying you'll kill someone

36:11.670 --> 36:12.740
and actually doing it

36:12.760 --> 36:13.840
are two different things.

36:14.830 --> 36:15.810
Besides,

36:16.510 --> 36:17.670
you knew we needed to get

36:17.670 --> 36:19.070
Cold Spring Palace's scheme out of her,

36:19.730 --> 36:21.740
so you wouldn't kill her at that moment.

36:23.850 --> 36:24.880
Alright.

36:25.670 --> 36:26.710
Don't blame yourself.

36:27.620 --> 36:29.700
You're not a cold-hearted machine.

36:30.080 --> 36:31.600
You're a living, breathing person.

36:38.470 --> 36:41.610
♫When you engrave your love into my heart♫

36:41.840 --> 36:45.040
♫When my star falls only for you♫

36:45.790 --> 36:47.430
♫When the heavens fall♫

36:47.990 --> 36:52.940
♫I can still connect with you through the waning moon♫

36:53.300 --> 36:56.180
♫When my pain blurs my eyes♫

36:56.750 --> 37:00.690
♫Out of the countless stars, I see only you♫

37:00.280 --> 37:01.160
Thank you.

37:01.380 --> 37:10.200
♫As you turn into a falling star and crash into my heart♫

37:02.350 --> 37:03.190
Mu.

37:05.460 --> 37:06.380
I'm fine now.

37:07.930 --> 37:08.820
Really?

37:14.780 --> 37:16.140
We can't afford to lose

37:17.040 --> 37:18.210
the battle in the Outlanders' City.

37:20.590 --> 37:21.830
We won't lose.

37:25.780 --> 37:28.110
Cold Spring Palace is indeed colluding with the Outlanders.

37:28.670 --> 37:29.420
Tian Huo.

37:29.440 --> 37:30.230
Did you recognize

37:30.230 --> 37:31.400
who that person in black was?

37:32.020 --> 37:33.570
His spiritual power is on par with mine.

37:33.920 --> 37:35.950
At first, I suspected it was Hua Lin,

37:36.060 --> 37:37.900
but the techniques didn't match.

37:38.100 --> 37:39.830
Could it be Wu Zhao?

37:40.010 --> 37:41.970
Wu Zhao, though the deputy general to the King,

37:42.000 --> 37:43.380
isn't that powerful.

37:43.620 --> 37:45.180
But that was seven years ago.

37:45.860 --> 37:47.320
What if something's changed

37:47.530 --> 37:49.090
in these seven years?

37:50.340 --> 37:51.790
The upcoming Fenlan Banquet

37:52.110 --> 37:53.630
is definitely a trap.

37:54.210 --> 37:55.330
But no matter what,

37:55.730 --> 37:58.070
the vision from the Contemplation Stone must come true.

37:58.130 --> 37:59.080
We must get

37:59.110 --> 38:00.390
all three Heart Flames.

38:01.430 --> 38:02.680
That means

38:03.100 --> 38:04.310
we must

38:04.580 --> 38:05.630
attend that banquet.

38:06.690 --> 38:07.810
Shuo is right.

38:08.070 --> 38:08.800
We must attend it.

38:15.170 --> 38:15.840
It's late.

38:15.840 --> 38:17.080
You asked me out alone.

38:17.220 --> 38:18.070
What is it?

38:18.400 --> 38:19.770
There are too many people in the inn.

38:19.800 --> 38:20.760
I asked you out

38:20.780 --> 38:22.260
to ask if you got anything

38:22.290 --> 38:23.120
out of Fu Ling tonight.

38:23.150 --> 38:24.460
Before we could get anything out of her,

38:24.480 --> 38:25.960
Fu Ling was rescued by someone.

38:26.050 --> 38:28.060
Who could rescue her from the hands of Bright Moon Palace?

38:28.080 --> 38:29.130
The person who helped her

38:29.160 --> 38:30.250
could use spiritual power.

38:30.820 --> 38:31.720
An Outlander?

38:32.420 --> 38:34.360
I searched the city tonight.

38:34.390 --> 38:35.060
No other demons

38:35.080 --> 38:35.890
from Cold Spring Palace

38:35.920 --> 38:36.920
other than Fu Ling.

38:37.820 --> 38:40.100
But the fact that an Outlander openly came to her rescue

38:40.280 --> 38:41.320
means someone high-ranking

38:41.320 --> 38:43.500
in the Outlander Race is colluding with Cold Spring Palace.

38:44.430 --> 38:45.800
Tomorrow's banquet is not just a banquet.

38:45.820 --> 38:47.230
I'll send you away now.

38:47.250 --> 38:48.070
No.

38:48.240 --> 38:49.240
Shuo.

38:49.290 --> 38:50.890
Can you stop being so willful?

38:51.030 --> 38:51.890
I told you,

38:52.090 --> 38:53.450
you don't need to worry about me.

38:53.840 --> 38:55.150
When will you understand

38:55.170 --> 38:56.970
that I'm no longer the same Bai Shuo from Ning'an City?

38:58.340 --> 38:59.790
Miss, sir.

39:01.260 --> 39:02.810
Stop arguing.

39:02.830 --> 39:04.960
Play with the dough instead.

39:24.070 --> 39:24.920
Good girl.

39:25.670 --> 39:26.870
We won't argue anymore.

39:27.390 --> 39:28.910
Give this to Shuo.

39:29.500 --> 39:30.980
She loved playing with it when she was little.

39:54.360 --> 39:55.130
Zhao.

39:55.150 --> 39:55.540
I...

39:55.560 --> 39:56.210
It's late.

39:59.380 --> 40:00.500
Go back now.

40:11.350 --> 40:14.010
My relationship with Cold Spring Palace must stay hidden.

40:14.270 --> 40:16.360
You have to dress the wound yourself.

40:18.700 --> 40:19.810
Thank you, General.

40:39.770 --> 40:41.630
The Fenlan Banquet is tomorrow.

40:41.950 --> 40:43.030
Before that,

40:43.170 --> 40:44.920
His Majesty doesn't want any more mistakes.

40:45.330 --> 40:46.650
Lady Fu Ling,

40:46.670 --> 40:48.310
please stay here for recovery.

40:48.340 --> 40:50.050
Is this the will of the King

40:50.570 --> 40:52.140
or yours?

40:52.610 --> 40:53.750
Does it make a difference?

41:00.890 --> 41:02.590
Not really.

41:02.860 --> 41:05.310
Hua Lin can never imagine

41:05.480 --> 41:06.330
that you

41:06.360 --> 41:08.300
are my master's true ally,

41:08.330 --> 41:10.490
while he's merely a decoy,

41:10.510 --> 41:11.760
a decoy

41:11.840 --> 41:12.910
to shield you

41:12.930 --> 41:14.450
from suspicion and harm.

41:14.870 --> 41:16.350
I must thank you, General,

41:16.370 --> 41:17.850
for revealing the location of the City

41:17.880 --> 41:19.630
so Grand Master could plan ahead.

41:19.660 --> 41:21.580
I need to thank your master for giving me the pill

41:21.780 --> 41:23.450
that boosted my spiritual power.

41:24.840 --> 41:26.270
You're being too modest, General.

41:26.370 --> 41:27.470
In terms of strength,

41:27.700 --> 41:28.920
military achievements,

41:28.950 --> 41:30.190
bravery, and foresight,

41:30.570 --> 41:32.540
Hua Lin is no match for you.

41:33.800 --> 41:35.280
He was born weak,

41:35.360 --> 41:37.260
yet the Mei family would rather sacrifice their patriarch

41:37.280 --> 41:38.520
than let someone else take the throne,

41:38.540 --> 41:40.230
just because he's of royal blood.

41:40.260 --> 41:41.260
If I were you,

41:41.280 --> 41:42.120
I'd never accept it either.

41:42.830 --> 41:44.380
I know you've been hunkering down

41:44.410 --> 41:45.560
for many years.

41:45.740 --> 41:47.320
At the Banquet tomorrow,

41:47.490 --> 41:49.140
we'll reap the rewards together.

41:59.110 --> 42:00.380
Don't go to the Banquet?

42:02.190 --> 42:02.900
Bai Shuo.

42:02.930 --> 42:04.660
What are you talking about?

42:05.220 --> 42:06.390
I know what you're doing.

42:06.770 --> 42:08.440
You're saying the Banquet is dangerous

42:08.540 --> 42:10.700
to trick us into giving up

42:10.730 --> 42:13.350
so you can take the third Heart Flame for yourself,

42:13.510 --> 42:14.280
right?

42:14.300 --> 42:15.900
-Exactly.
-That's it.

42:15.930 --> 42:17.590
We're representatives from various sects.

42:17.610 --> 42:19.400
Although we can't use magic here,

42:19.460 --> 42:20.730
we have the backing of our sects

42:20.750 --> 42:21.870
outside the City.

42:21.890 --> 42:23.410
Who dares do anything to us?

42:23.440 --> 42:24.930
-Yes.
-Exactly.

42:25.590 --> 42:27.130
I've said what I need to say.

42:27.150 --> 42:28.340
You can believe me or not.

42:28.370 --> 42:29.450
Whether you go to your doom

42:29.480 --> 42:30.410
is up to you.

42:30.430 --> 42:31.030
Stop!

42:31.030 --> 42:32.230
What are you talking about?

42:43.810 --> 42:44.960
Anyone sensible

42:44.990 --> 42:46.810
can see the situation in the Outlanders' City.

42:47.160 --> 42:48.510
Since the Outlanders' Tomb,

42:48.530 --> 42:50.770
this has ceased to be just a simple contest.

42:51.150 --> 42:52.590
If it weren't for me and the Master of Bright Moon Palace

42:52.630 --> 42:53.810
breaking Rong Xian's realm of resentment,

42:53.830 --> 42:55.710
do you think you could even stand here now?

42:55.760 --> 42:56.760
One wrong move,

42:56.800 --> 42:57.910
and we'll all die

42:58.030 --> 42:59.480
in the Outlanders' City.

43:03.410 --> 43:04.660
The three Heart Flames

43:04.690 --> 43:06.480
are absolutely going to Bright Moon Palace.

43:06.630 --> 43:08.360
Since you don't stand a chance,

43:08.380 --> 43:09.790
why take the risk?

43:10.030 --> 43:10.550
You...

43:10.570 --> 43:12.220
Don't look down on us.

43:12.250 --> 43:13.290
-Yes.
-Yeah.

43:13.310 --> 43:14.260
Calm down.

43:14.590 --> 43:16.380
I'm not looking down on anyone.

43:16.410 --> 43:18.440
I'm just trying to make you see reality.

43:18.840 --> 43:19.630
Whether you live or die

43:19.630 --> 43:20.840
has nothing to do with me.

43:20.950 --> 43:22.150
The reason I'm here

43:22.150 --> 43:23.550
wasting my breath

43:23.550 --> 43:25.360
is because I think there are still some…

43:27.650 --> 43:29.280
kind people among you.

43:29.390 --> 43:30.870
But that's all I can say.

43:31.340 --> 43:32.490
From here on out,

43:32.850 --> 43:34.140
you can walk

43:34.190 --> 43:35.480
whatever path you choose.

43:37.840 --> 43:39.150
Make it clear.

43:39.150 --> 43:40.440
What are you talking about?

43:43.480 --> 43:44.590
Is she trying to scare us?

43:44.590 --> 43:45.800
-Yes.
-Exactly.

43:48.760 --> 43:50.280
Will those Eternals and demons trust us?

43:50.650 --> 43:52.040
The ones who are afraid of death will.

43:52.200 --> 43:54.010
The ones who aren't won't believe anything we say.

43:56.000 --> 43:57.920
There are three visions from the Contemplation Stone.

43:57.950 --> 43:59.500
The first two have come true.

43:59.530 --> 44:01.240
There's just one left.

44:01.680 --> 44:04.260
That is, me holding all three Heart Flames, along with the mons…

44:06.590 --> 44:07.340
Hua Yong.

44:07.490 --> 44:08.700
We'll be here together.

44:08.890 --> 44:09.890
Where is this?

44:10.110 --> 44:11.410
The Underground Palace.

44:11.440 --> 44:13.080
It's where the Outlander King's Sword is kept.

44:13.190 --> 44:14.200
At the Banquet,

44:14.230 --> 44:15.290
I'll find a way to get inside there.

44:15.660 --> 44:16.780
I'll go with you.

44:16.850 --> 44:17.660
-No.
-No.
